    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201780/extras/690a3b21b09d2d8dbd3a0a48f6954417.poster.avif?t=1755109949\" width=616 height=148 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201780/extras/690a3b21b09d2d8dbd3a0a48f6954417.webm?t=1755109949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201780/extras/690a3b21b09d2d8dbd3a0a48f6954417.mp4?t=1755109949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>击败所有挡你去路的敌人，杀死吸血鬼王国「蒸汽血脉」的女王内莉莎，在她的咬噬让你彻底沦为恶魔仆从之前！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201780/extras/a3da76d684d1eeda9f19a4ab03905792.webp?t=1755109949\" width=616 height=48 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201780/extras/d512afe3fd2a2c1dfe92c3d02efd307c.poster.avif?t=1755109949\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201780/extras/d512afe3fd2a2c1dfe92c3d02efd307c.webm?t=1755109949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201780/extras/d512afe3fd2a2c1dfe92c3d02efd307c.mp4?t=1755109949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>从自动贩卖机中购买饮品，击败头目后还能获得他们身上的强大力量。每次战斗前，你的义姐卡珊德拉都会在头目战入口等你，向你贩售关键道具。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201780/extras/bb94d5405035dfaaecd37a4729d5d0d1.webp?t=1755109949\" width=616 height=48 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201780/extras/476fe5f3f8c82c1b3bd0467f2065a1b9.poster.avif?t=1755109949\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201780/extras/476fe5f3f8c82c1b3bd0467f2065a1b9.webm?t=1755109949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201780/extras/476fe5f3f8c82c1b3bd0467f2065a1b9.mp4?t=1755109949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>从养母梅琳达手中领取起始车票，选择任意一座城堡作为你的起点。在关卡之间，列车员麦克会随机提供路线选项，由你决定接下来前往哪座城堡。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201780/extras/2165f74e9a8f6c3e7554f574c4ce85b2.webp?t=1755109949\" width=616 height=48 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201780/extras/0af9798672b9e235bf5666ddd25dd9ba.poster.avif?t=1755109949\" width=616 height=148 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201780/extras/0af9798672b9e235bf5666ddd25dd9ba.webm?t=1755109949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201780/extras/0af9798672b9e235bf5666ddd25dd9ba.mp4?t=1755109949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>迎战五位各具特色、强大无比的头目王者，他们分别统治着不同的城堡！",
